# Static archive of GameCon 1998 (reconstructed from the Internet Archive).
#
# GameCon 1998 ran in OLOMOUC. It was a SECTION of the whole altar.cz publisher
# site (path altar.cz/gamecon/), the same path-era as 1999-2005 — older than
# the gamecon.altar.cz subdomain (2006-2008).
#
# This is the EARLIEST GameCon year on Wayback. What genuinely survives, and is
# served here:
#   - the GameCon 1998 homepage exactly as captured (Dec 1998, title
#     "Gamecon 1998", "Gamecon 1998 již skončil … jména vítězů na této stránce"),
#   - the Mistrovství v DrD + tournament RESULTS: vysledky98 (real 1998 results).
# 1998 had no separate program/tournament pages on the web — they 404.
#
# The homepage's year-logo originally used a thumbnail GIF (small.logo1998.gif)
# that Wayback never captured; we point the thumbnail at the full logo1998.jpg
# (the only surviving 1998 logo image), scaled down.
#
# Pages restored from web.archive.org, transcoded WINDOWS-1250 -> UTF-8 (with an
# injected <meta charset>; the source declared charset only via the HTTP header).
# Dead ad embeds (Mr.Lin(x), billboard.cz) stripped. Dynamic CGI -> themed 404.

DirectoryIndex index.html
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

Options -Indexes

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME}/index.html -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteRule ^$  index.html [L]

    RewriteRule ^.*$ - [R=404,L]
</IfModule>
